@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kffcqj(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (tmp - wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.89)))
    tmp = v1
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v1 + 0.95)) - ((v1 + 0.02 + tmp + 0.35) * (v2 + 0.40 / v1 + 0.59)))
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.30 * tmp + 0.48)) - (wp.cos(v1 + 0.98) / 0.78))
    tmp = (v0 * wp.sin(wp.exp(v1 + 0.57)))
    data[tid] = v0
